Subject: [PATCH] ALSA: hda - add codec support for Kabylake display audio codec
Git-commit: 91815d8aa7e2f45d30e51caa297061ad893628d9
Patch-mainline: 4.5-rc1
References: bsc#996790

This patch adds codec ID (0x8086280b) for Kabylake display codec
and apply the hsw fix-ups to Kabylake.

Signed-off-by: Libin Yang <libin.yang@linux.intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

